          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1654645-deb-readerbuzz-nance?shelf=sci-fi-fantasy">sci-fi-fantasy</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1654645-deb-readerbuzz-nance?shelf=children-s-books">children-s-books</a>, 
