        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2306053832" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8515920672394019086"><i>The Devil’s Arithmetic</i> is a moving and heartbreaking young adult fantasy/historical fiction novella grounded in the real events that happened during the Holocaust. However, I found the first half of the book to be tortuously slow and boring.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


