<span id="freeTextContainer2215536299005839137">A poignant story of life in a concentration camp through the eyes of a young girl. Amazing writing for this part of the story! I did not like the &quot;time travel&quot; aspect of the book, but the historical portions were very well done.</span>
  <span id="freeText2215536299005839137" style="display:none">A poignant story of life in a concentration camp through the eyes of a young girl. Amazing writing for this part of the story! I did not like the "time travel" aspect of the book, but the historical portions were very well done.</span>
